{"tid":2169672,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［永不忘記］菲律賓人質事件十週年悼念區","createTime":"2020-08-22T16:28:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-24T12:31:23.000Z","uid":325346,"like":84,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":46,"replies":[{"pid":"b848ff029e065bb3c21f1ab4892a44f802ffb215","tid":2169672,"uid":325346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T16:28:40.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong><span class=\"red\">永世不去菲律賓</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n悼 <br />\n\\|/<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n傅卓仁<br />\n謝廷駿Masa領隊<br />\n楊綺華<br />\n楊綺琴<br />\n汪子林<br />\n梁頌儀<br />\n梁頌詩<br />\n梁錦榮<br />\n<br />\n轉眼間十年，畫面仍瀝瀝在目<br />\n以前我們會屌、睇到菲仔菲妹在現場打卡的笑面<br />\n但而家香港黑警會在示威場地打卡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n當日曾特首已經盡力搵阿基諾三世<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n奈何我們唔係國家<br />\n曾特首任內最盡力的一件事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢係為香港人的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n十年過去、汪氏姐弟好似大學畢業了<br />\n梁家的男丁不知情況如何<br />\n<br />\n比較開心見到易小玲在台灣做左整容手術、可以食返野、香港的整形水平不及台灣<br />\n<br />\n每一年都希望大家記住823<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8db9212817379b8d8301f455e6b96b9480749451","tid":2169672,"uid":106276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T16:29:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6979083c6159ae3534c1a3868223d4d310156b4c","tid":2169672,"uid":48362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T16:30:24.000Z","msg":"菲律賓警察 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hk